# Project Scalene — environment variables
#
# Copy to `.env` (gitignored) and fill in real values. Never commit `.env`
# or any real secret value — this file documents keys only.

# docs/ARCHITECTURE.md sec18.3 (STORY-1503): enables URLScanner's real
# external reputation check (URLhaus, abuse.ch) alongside the always-on
# local heuristics. Free to obtain: https://auth.abuse.ch/
# Unset: URLScanner falls back to local-heuristics-only (composite_check()
# degrades cleanly, never a doomed unauthenticated request).
SCALENE_URLHAUS_AUTH_KEY=
